---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="py-12 bg-black border-t border-zinc-800 text-zinc-500 text-sm">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6">
      
      <!-- Logo & Copyright -->
      <div class="text-center md:text-left">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start gap-2 mb-2">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-zinc-900 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-orange-500">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.25 6.75 22.5 12l-5.25 5.25m-10.5 0L1.5 12l5.25-5.25m7.5-3-4.5 16.5" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-zinc-300 font-bold text-lg tracking-wide">Wektor Kodu</span>
        </div>
        <p>&copy; {currentYear} <a href="https://wektor-kodu.vercel.app" target="_blank" class="hover:text-teal-400 transition-colors">Wektor Kodu</a>. Wszelkie prawa zastrzeżone.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Social Icons (Placeholders) -->
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 bg-zinc-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-zinc-800 hover:text-orange-500 transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-facebook"><path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 bg-zinc-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-zinc-800 hover:text-orange-500 transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-instagram"><rect width="20" height="20" x="2" y="2" rx="5" ry="5"/><path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"/><line x1="17.5" x2="17.51" y1="6.5" y2="6.5"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Legal Text -->
    <div class="mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-zinc-900 text-center md:text-left text-xs text-zinc-600 max-w-3xl">
      <p>
        Serwis prowadzony w ramach działalności nierejestrowanej przez: [Twoje Imię i Nazwisko]. 
        Na każdą usługę wystawiam imienny rachunek zwolniony z podatku VAT.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
